message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this great product! I think you'll really love it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $140.
Hi Alice, thanks for the offer! I'm interested, but $140 is a bit more than I was hoping to spend. Would you be willing to do $130?
I understand you're looking for a good deal, Bob. I can do $135, but that's as low as I can go.
